{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/blog/2021-01-04-introducing-berlin-cricket-academy/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"3c1cc7f8-47d7-51db-8089-c8e5fcbac92f","html":"<p>Since 2021, Berlin Cricket Academy has been finding and featuring some of the best players in the Berlin area. From coaching them on the ins-and-outs of the sport to honing their athletic skills, we're proud to teach not only the love of the game, but to also impart the ideals of good sportsmanship, teamwork and loyalty. Berlin Cricket Academy aspires to be a competitive force in Germany. We hone raw talent to maturity with quality coaching and primal workouts. Teamwork, perseverance, sportsmanship - those are the hallmarks of Berlin Cricket Academy.</p>","frontmatter":{"date":"January 04, 2021","title":"Introducing Berlin Cricket Academy","description":"Champion athletes aren't just born - they're selected, trained, molded and tested.","tags":["cricket"],"featuredimage":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.3580901856763925,"src":"/static/4a436785f188547b8268507a25f4e9ae/5dbbf/cricket-bw.jpg","srcSet":"/static/4a436785f188547b8268507a25f4e9ae/89b9c/cricket-bw.jpg 512w,\n/static/4a436785f188547b8268507a25f4e9ae/26852/cricket-bw.jpg 1024w,\n/static/4a436785f188547b8268507a25f4e9ae/5dbbf/cricket-bw.jpg 2048w,\n/static/4a436785f188547b8268507a25f4e9ae/613b6/cricket-bw.jpg 3072w,\n/static/4a436785f188547b8268507a25f4e9ae/fd08d/cricket-bw.jpg 3600w","sizes":"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"id":"3c1cc7f8-47d7-51db-8089-c8e5fcbac92f"}},"staticQueryHashes":["4080856488"]}